quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Gom…óii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi Anndu…ďe mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"Ko hon…óum woni …óii nanndonlaaji nate mahii…óe, …óin …ói ufini…óon e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen no rewde …ói"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"Gom…óii on laatike onon e baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen e nder majjere …ďanngunde won…óon"
  21,55,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addan…óaa men, kaa an ko e fijoo…ďe …ďen jeya…óaa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin On Tagu…óo…ói, min komi jeyaa…óo e seedii…ďe …ďen e dow …óum"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii …óii sanamuuji mo'on …ďaawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ruŇčii …ďe"
  21,58,"O wa…ói …ói kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, belajo'o kam…ďe …ďe ruttoto e mayru"
  21,59,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko hommbo wa…ói …óu'un e rewetee…ói amen …óin? Pellet, on ko o jeyaa…óo e too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  21,60,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men naniino suka no jaŇčtoo …ói ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"
  21,61,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Addee mo yeeso gite yim…ďe …ďen, belajo'o …ďe seedoto"
  21,62,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Enee, Ibraahiima ko an wa…ói …óu'um …óoo e rewetee…ói amen …óin"
  21,63,"O maaki: \"Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle …óum, lanndee…ói si tawii …ói laatike hi…ói wowla"
  21,64,"∆Āe ruttii faade e wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"Pellet, ko onon woni too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  21,65,"Refti …ďe uggini ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen […ďe wi'i:] gom…óii hi…óa anndi …ói'i wonaa wowlay…ói"
  21,66,"O maaki: \"Enee, on reway gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e huunde hara lorrataa on kadi"
  21,67,Bis mo'on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,68,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Sunnee mo, wallee rewetee…ói mo'on …óin, si tawii ko on golloo…ďe"
  21,69,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo yiite, laato …ďuu…ďol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima"
  21,70,∆Āe faandanii mo pewje Men wa…ói …ďe pertube …ďen
  21,71,"Men danndi mo [Men danndi kadi] Luutu faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barkini e mu'un wonannde tageefooji …óin"
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka …ďeydugol, kala ma…ď…ďe Men wa…ói […ďe] mo∆ī∆īu…ďe"
  21,73,"Men wa…ói …ďe Almaamii…ďe hi…ďe fewna e Yamiroore Amen Men Wahayini faade e ma…ď…ďe gollugol mo∆ī∆īi …óin e √Īinnugol Julde nden e Okkugol Jakka on, …ďe laatinoke ko …ďe Reway …ďe Men"
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo √Ďee√Īal e Ganndal, Men danndi mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yim…ďe mu'un] laatinoo no golla so…ďu…ói …óin, pellet, kam…ďe …ďe laatinoke yim…ďe bon…ďe faasiqii…ďe"
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen"